data.description: Welcome to 9838 Charline Ln. This truly exceptional home features a  flexible floor plan with a welcoming interior and a flow-through living and dining area to include an eat-in kitchen, as well as a formal dining room that can easily be transformed into an extra living space, office, or home gym as shown in photos!      Entertaining has never been easier thanks to this cozy, eat-in kitchen that been recently updated to include recessed lighting and granite countertops. Located conveniently off of the kitchen is the light enhancing sliding doors bringing you into your backyard oasis, where you can enjoy a peaceful atmosphere equipped with a large patio, lush lawn and trees yielding pomegranates and almonds!     Upstairs, you'll find a cozy loft space, perfect for a home office or additional play area, and three bedrooms.  The generous main bedroom is roomy and comfortable, and features a spacious bathroom, and his-and-hers walk-in closets. Adding to the home's charm are newly-installed carpeting floors throughout the second floor, new HVAC as of summer 2022, and new roof as of December 2020. With an exceptional location in an established area of Far West Side with NO HOA!  Enjoy active living at its finest! Easy travel throughout the city thanks to easy access of the main highway nearby! Come see for yourself!
